  "body": "<p>This Pull Request updates dependency <a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/eslint-config-prettier\">eslint-config-prettier</a> from <code>v2.5.0</code> to <code>v2.6.0</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"commits\">Commits</h3>\n<p><details><br />\n<summary>prettier/eslint-config-prettier</summary></p>\n<h4 id=\"260\">2.6.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/eslint-config-prettier/commit/0bfb266df652850857dc0340af41e6bc2a43434f\"><code>0bfb266</code></a> eslint-config-prettier v2.6.0</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/eslint-config-prettier/commit/7d7786b23ebf284dc75f90afd49ae49a5180d1ad\"><code>7d7786b</code></a> Use https for all eslint.org links</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/prettier/eslint-config-prettier/commit/e47c6a6de6c3fae40f561759cb9fab79453db816\"><code>e47c6a6</code></a> Turn off no-floating-decimal</li>\n</ul>\n<p></details></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This PR has been generated by <a href=\"https://renovateapp.com\">Renovate Bot</a>.</p>",
